## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| AI model training time/accuracy | High | High | Demo mode as fallback; use pre-trained weights |
| Render free tier cold starts (30s) | High | Medium | Frontend loading spinner; retry logic |
| Razorpay KYC delay for live payments | Medium | High | Use test mode for development; start KYC early |
| MongoDB 512MB Atlas free tier limit | Medium | Medium | Archive old detections/bids; upgrade at scale |
| Web Speech API browser support | High | Low | Manual input fallback always available |
| i18n translation quality (Marathi) | Medium | Medium | Native speaker review; community contribution |
| Socket.IO scaling on free Render | Medium | Medium | Connection limiting; upgrade for production |

---

## Definition of Done

A feature is complete when:
1. API endpoint returns correct responses with edge case handling
2. UI renders correctly on Chrome, Firefox, Safari (desktop + mobile)
3. Feature works in all 3 languages (English, Hindi, Marathi)
4. Loading and error states are handled in UI
5. Code is committed to main branch with meaningful commit message
6. Manual QA pass on staging deployment


